[h1]Changelog[/h1]

[h2]v0.1.0 — 2026-03-18[/h2]
[b]Initial scaffold[/b]

[list]
[*] POSnet radio channel registration at configurable frequency
[*] Procedural mission generation from registered templates
[*] 5 mission categories: Industrial Recovery, Vehicle Salvage, Scientific Research, Survivor Assistance, Infrastructure Repair
[*] 4 difficulty levels: Easy, Medium, Hard, Critical
[*] Extensible completion detector with item_acquire built-in checker
[*] Player-side operation log with persistence in modData
[*] Server-side timed broadcast system
[*] 6 sandbox options for full configurability
[*] CI pipeline with 9 automated checks
[/list]
